        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Millionaire Peach Salad. A British home-cook's dish, the kind of recipe families adjust across generations. Serves 4.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A salad in the everyday register, dressed at the table, leaves dry, dressing emulsified before it meets the bowl.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
